jectives for MDPs. We\nconsider the canonical parity objectives for $\\omega$-regular objectives, and\nfor parity objectives with $d$-priorities we present an algorithm that computes\nthe almost-sure winning region with $\\widetilde{O}(n^{2-\\epsilon})$ symbolic\noperations and $\\widetilde{O}(n^{\\epsilon})$ symbolic space, for all $0 <\n\\epsilon \\leq 1/2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Apr 2021 13:53:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-16"}
